attributes.title: I’m disappointed in you mr.cheeto ✨👹🥱❤️
attributes.review: This app is atrocious. I can not believe an app like this is allowed to be on the App Store, Shame on you mr.cheeto (prez [𝑢𝑛𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑡𝑎𝑡𝑒𝑙𝑦]) This app kept crashing and everyday sent me very interesting...𝑢ℎ.. 𝑁𝑜𝑡𝑖𝑓𝑖𝑐𝑎𝑡𝑖𝑜𝑛𝑠✨. For example, on the first day I got this app I’ve been sent a picture of oranges and hot Cheetos.  —- oh my apologies i meant the president (although there’s no difference) anyways what I’m trying to say is I am now legally blind from taking even a glance at those pictures. I have never been the same I can not even take a look at hot Cheetos or oranges when I’m shopping for groceries.. 𝑌𝑒𝑠 𝑞𝑢𝑖𝑡𝑒 𝑢𝑛𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑡𝑢𝑛𝑎𝑡𝑒. Anyways I’m to tired to go through all the problems I came across while using this app. I am now heading to the eye doctor to hopefully get glasses or contacts. But as I said before I will never be the same again as I keep having flashbacks of this orange president we have.. Anyways have a good day all of you👹✨👁👄👁.
